Miscellaneous Highlights: The Spurs won by a score of 109-106.
Others: Victor Wembanyama had ten points, three rebounds, one assist and two blocks while shooting 4/6 from the field and 2/3 from the three-point range in his first ten minutes of playing time.
Wembanyama finished the loss with 17 points, nine rebounds, one assist and one block while shooting 5/18 from the field and 1/8 from the three-point range in 28 minutes of playing time.
The Rockets are 1-1 in their first two games after blowing out the Memphis Grizzlies by a score of 128-108 on Friday evening.
Following Saturday's showdown, the Rockets and Spurs will face off (again) on Monday evening in San Antonio.
